description: Soak in the views of Seattle in this beautiful 17th floor condo! Enjoy the sights of the city and the Sound from any corner of the light-filled unit. This rare, upper-level corner unit offers 3 spacious bedrooms and an expansive open space. Amenities include a new indoor pool, hot tub, sauna, fitness center, and more. Recent updates include new hardwood flooring, carpet, and appliances. Secured indoor parking garage includes a private storage room and 2 parking spots. Central and convenient location with a walk score of 97! Commute to downtown in minutes. HOA covers all utilities.
